==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Copple
<hw>Cop"ple</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[A dim. of
<er>Cop</er>.]</ety> <def>Something rising in a conical shape;
specifically, a hill rising to a point.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A low cape, and upon it a <qex>copple</qex> not very high.</q>
<rj><qau>Hakluyt.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Copple-crown</ent>⟦br⟧
